{"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "当义经带着宝巫迦、梓兰和政宗赶到现场时，看到的就是空爆跪在月见夜身边，失魂落魄的样子。"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "月见......夜？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰姐，你们来了！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#15$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他还没死，但是状况很不好！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#15$2"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们听到了“雷之主”的吼叫声，立刻赶了过来！", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底发生了什么！", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#5$2"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不知道，等我赶到的时候，就看到“雷之主”......", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#13$2"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“雷之主”......是它把月见夜变成这样的吗！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "空爆", "content": "我......不知道，"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "空爆", "content": "但我看到了！它......它在用你的力量！"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和你在宫里净化尸体时一模一样！它把那些野兽的黑气......都吸进自己身体里了！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#8$2"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你说什么？！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不......不可能......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#10$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的吗？！你不会看错了喵？", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$4"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_dog_voice1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyD_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（肯定的低吼）", "name": "义经"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyD_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它......它不仅杀了母亲......还夺走了属于她的巫女的力量......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是了，原来是这样，难怪它能逆转吾打开的门，难怪它能够召来咒鬼......", "n